OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with largely clear skies,
OL,7,Falthough a veil of high cloud will
OL,8,Fmove over at times. A patchy rural
OL,9,Ffrost is possible in sheltered spots,
OL,10,Fbut most places staying above freezing
OL,11,Fwith a brisk wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,14,Facross the region. After a chilly
OL,15,Fstart, it will warm up through the
OL,16,Fday, though still holding onto brisk
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
