OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMore
OL,6,Fhumid on Friday with showers possible.
OL,7,FTurning increasingly cloudy through
OL,8,Fthe weekend with an increasing risk of
OL,9,Frain and heavy showers, possibly
OL,10,Fthundery.
